com.here.android.mpa.guidance

Class NavigationManager.LaneInfoListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.here.android.mpa.guidance.NavigationManager.LaneInfoListener
  • Enclosing class:
    NavigationManager
    Deprecated. 
    As of SDK 3.2. Use NavigationManager.LaneInformationListener instead.

    @Deprecated
public abstract static class NavigationManager.LaneInfoListener
extends java.lang.Object
    LaneInfoListener provides callback of lane info related events from NavigationManager. By default, empty implementations are provided for each callback method, users may selectively overload specific methods that are of interest.

    No callback will be triggered if the HERE license key is invalid.
